data.description: Beautiful, 3 bedroom 2.5 bath, Craftsman style home. Covered front porch with stone pillars.  Gorgeous kitchen with stainless steel appliances with plenty of cabinet space and a breakfast bar. Master bedroom is on the main floor with 2 additional nice size bedrooms on the second floor.  Master bathroom has master bathroom with double sink vanity and walk-in closet.  Beautiful wood floors. Main floor laundry. From the kitchen you can walk out on to the patio. Detached one car garage with long driveway.
